804\/black-and-white-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21193804\/black-and-white-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21193804\/black-and-white-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21193804\/black-and-white-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A bedroom with a black wall and 3D art that makes this space come alive\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Charming Checkers In Black And White&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for a black and white bedroom design? If yes then we have just the one for you. This bedroom has been designed with a dark wall and a bed with black and white checked sheets. The bed has a headboard covered with a checkered sheet to match the bed&#8217;s attire. This bedroom theme can be used in your kid&#8217;s room or even in yours. This bedroom comes with an armchair with a rounded black body and white legs. To deck this bedroom up a little more, there is a globe in pitch black placed on the shelf in the bedroom. White candles add to the decor along with mini white vases with lush green plants: Black and white frames with a punch of yellow pep this bedroom up.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21194752\/charming-checkers-black-and-white-bedroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Charming checkers black and white bedroom design designed with a dark wall and a bed \" class=\"wp-image-18511\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21194752\/charming-checkers-black-and-white-bedroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21194752\/charming-checkers-black-and-white-bedroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-con