m-black-and-white-wall-painting.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21195147\/bedroom-black-and-white-wall-painting-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21195147\/bedroom-black-and-white-wall-painting-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21195147\/bedroom-black-and-white-wall-painting-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A black and white themed bedroom with wooden flooring a white floor rug and a white lampshade\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">&nbsp;It\u2019s A Striped Little World In This Bedroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you absolutely adore stripes, then this bedroom design is made for you. This bedroom comes with striped bedding in black and white. The sheets and the pillows are all stipped. This bedroom also has black and white bedroom furniture, Take a look at the side table stand in black &#8211; it acts as a solid surface to keep your jugs. If you feel like sitting and reading for a change then there is a chair made from cane painted in black to support you. On the headboard rest two mini vases with a black and white pattern that go hand in hand with the whole striped theme.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21203113\/black-and-white-bedroom-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white bedroom furniture that comes with striped bedding \" class=\"wp-image-18513\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21203113\/black-and-white-bedroom-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21203113\/black-and-white-bedroom-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/21203113\/black-and-white-bedroom-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https